name: THE NIFTY BABY (Original gif)
description:
The Nifty Baby is a fundamental element of my collection. He is not widely known as he was overtaken by the Nyan Cat at one point, but he dates from the same time.
This is the first historic mint in this gif, and I think the whole world will remember this day.
This is the gif of the legendary video that made a splash on YT
Indeed, in the near future (if future there is) there will be many variations and remixes of this gif, and may even be propelled to number one rank on the cryptomemes podium.
This will all depend in part on you, and your ability to use this meme under the right circumstances. He say a lot. For me it means something like:
"The world may be falling apart, I will continue to be happy."
...........
The origins:
I love this simple picture since ever. Tiny!
This is a photo of my daughter who is now 15 years old.
It was once when I went to pick her up from school.
She is always so cute, and this mint is for her.
